data.title: Southwest Missouri’s 457 names to know in high school sports entering 2024-25 school year
data.meta_description: Our annual list of the southwest Missouri athletes you need to know entering the 2024-25 academic calendar is here.
data.text:
The 2024-25 high school athletics season is almost here and we're looking forward to returning to the different venues and meeting the next great athletes in our area.

For the third year in a row, we compiled a list of names everyone in the region should get to know as they are destined to grab headlines.

The great thing about this list is that there are over 450 names and then there are hundreds more who are ready to make names for themselves throughout the year. We're excited to find them and help you get to know them as well.

Here are 457 names to know heading into the school year.

More: How conference realignment will reshape southwest Missouri high school football in 2024
